How to get started developing the app
=====================================

1) Get a running app locally
----------------------------

- Install Go

- Install Google App Engine SDK for Go

- go get golang.org/x/build

- cd golang.org/x/build/app && goapp serve


2) Checking how it works
------------------------

- curl 'http://localhost:8080/init' to create dashboard and packages

- curl 'http://localhost:8080/packages?kind=subrepo' to see that
  things are initialized

- in a browser: http://localhost:8080/?repo=golang.org%2Fx%2Farch# to
  see the arch subrepo

- curl 'http://localhost:8080/buildtest' to launch tests
